{"tid":1746584,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［英文巴絲入］寫信去哈佛要求取消陳肇始學位","createTime":"2019-11-22T20:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:48:35.000Z","uid":190239,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"416652100112011842c2c65065382a46e8017225","tid":1746584,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T20:25:51.000Z","msg":"陳肇始曾就讀<span style=\"color: red;\">聖保祿中學</span>，擁有<span style=\"color: red;\">英國曼徹斯特大學</span>教育碩士、<span style=\"color: red;\">美國哈佛大學</span>公共衛生碩士以及<span style=\"color: red;\">香港大學</span>哲學博士學位。<br />\nBy wiki<br />\n<br />\n呢條撚樣連山埃好快散都講得出<br />\n我極度質疑佢嘅學位資格<br />\n有冇英文勁嘅手足可以draft封信<br />\n逐間send email 去學校追擊佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d92dbfc5ba33d274215d25ad7ad5e949285ff5b","tid":1746584,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:09:51.000Z","msg":"Twitter問會唔會快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3fac8d0dad3630846fad35cad4c8324af6f32c","tid":1746584,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:12:35.000Z","msg":"Twitter 唔夠 official"},{"pid":"80c08a5c2da7024a5bb541d0f0b396ca9864ed28","tid":1746584,"uid":22919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:49:43.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"3ffd8cafb185eddd2530a73915ba29c592dc1498","tid":1746584,"uid":147629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:52:28.000Z","msg":"其實名譽學位（類似獎項）先收得返"},{"pid":"9bf5b2114ac2a4bdea853207bb80bf9cd4dab3ab","tid":1746584,"uid":147629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ffd8cafb185eddd2530a73915ba29c59